{"tid":1730083,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，個撚個淨係識喺度開post跪求","createTime":"2019-11-17T12:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T09:38:20.000Z","uid":52056,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c847bff032033cfa46396f90a2419fd2b87875","tid":1730083,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:22:55.000Z","msg":"依家成個飲食台都係跪求post叫人去食或者唔好食邊間<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母淨係識上連登跪有閪用</span></span><br />\n你估全世界咁得閒日日上連登mon post睇邊間食唔食得?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我攞啲舖名去地圖，去FB，去Openrice搵，除咗大家都識嗰啲臭朵之外一撚個都搵唔到啊屌你老味</span></span><br />\n個個爭住上連登開post，轉頭啲post就俾其他跪求post推到沈底冇人睇到<br />\n地圖就冇人update，大把人仲係懵盛盛食緊藍店/偽黃，冇澄清嘅黃店就冇人幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明過咗差唔多成半年，地圖/FB/IG/Openrice已經出咗好幾個，有啲巴打開，有啲同路人開<br />\n偏偏個個都仍然淨係識上嚟開啲除咗連登巴絲之外冇人睇嘅post<br />\n<strong>NeoGuideHK</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://neoguidehk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fneoguidehk.com%2F&d=sw6tlk2lcpT%2BYldK84vytJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=e1b1f9f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://neoguidehk.com/</a><br />\n<strong>香港人的飲食購物天地</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2701324926545942&d=sw6tlk2lcpT%2BYldK84vytJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=d9291b7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942</a><br />\n<strong>Restart HK 黃藍商戶整合</strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">啱啱上過好似502咗</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.restart-hk.com%2FShopList.html&d=sw6tlk2lcpT%2BYldK84vytJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=f65d52d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html</a><br />\n你班契弟開post求人之前唔該去報料，喺個post講報咗邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連報料都懶就咪鬼開post"},{"pid":"de5502552fd8ac9e515c78be22567ed2d2f429cd","tid":1730083,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96e311889de7705f8ae1cce82420cf0927b9eb6","tid":1730083,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea35ffaf951f9da15a58997756831fb1012cb81","tid":1730083,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有同路人開acc寫食評<br />\n巴絲有黃店推介可以試吓搵佢哋幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/restaurant/userinfo.htm?userid=66275053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Frestaurant%2Fuserinfo.htm%3Fuserid%3D66275053&d=sw6tlk2lcpT%2BYldK84vytJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=92375d3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/restaurant/userinfo.htm?userid=66275053</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/goodwest_standwithhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgoodwest_standwithhk%2F&d=sw6tlk2lcpT%2BYldK84vytJS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=a6edfd71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/goodwest_standwithhk/</a>"},{"pid":"23c3b10da916c3de9f034659f0bb45f11f5dc6be","tid":1730083,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:09:24.000Z","msg":"隔日再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95c7c4950a87ae60ee1c0c93f9016eecb2c32c0","tid":1730083,"uid":52056,"l